{"tid":409423,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"今年秋季觀眾票選最期待的電影，前3名是哪幾部電影？","createTime":"2017-09-22T04:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T06:24:51.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab128cee2978f3c7c539adf905f47cd66857db5","tid":409423,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T04:53:53.000Z","msg":"美國最大的電影預售網站Fandango，公布了旗下會員對秋季電影的期待性投票，結果一到三名，分別是今年的三部大片，從第三名到第一名分別是：<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.mvmv.com.tw/gallery/15119/photos_15119_1482397004_b54956e6c737823886200380bdc221cd.jpg?ts=501934546.7596667\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mvmv.com.tw%2Fgallery%2F15119%2Fphotos_15119_1482397004_b54956e6c737823886200380bdc221cd.jpg%3Fts%3D501934546.7596667&d=8W6UNhn1qrXi%2BJrxuTVLv6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f60ea4ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.mvmv.com.tw/gallery/15119/photos_15119_1482397004_b54956e6c737823886200380bdc221cd.jpg?ts=501934546.7596667</a><br />\n第三名《銀翼殺手2049》<br />\n<a href=\"http://img.hypesphere.com/20170109192955_74.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.hypesphere.com%2F20170109192955_74.jpg&d=8W6UNhn1qrXi%2BJrxuTVLv6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=34731dde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://img.hypesphere.com/20170109192955_74.jpg</a><br />\n第二名《正義聯盟》<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.mvmv.com.tw/gallery/13022/photos_13022_1491882699.jpg?ts=501934575.71966666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.mvmv.com.tw%2Fgallery%2F13022%2Fphotos_13022_1491882699.jpg%3Fts%3D501934575.71966666&d=8W6UNhn1qrXi%2BJrxuTVLv6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=d281141f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.mvmv.com.tw/gallery/13022/photos_13022_1491882699.jpg?ts=501934575.71966666</a><br />\n<br />\n第一名《雷神索爾3》<br />\n<br />\n這項數據調查有什麼影響？因為Fandango與票房極為相關，這也意即漫威的《雷神索爾3》目前看好度高於《正義聯盟》。而通常只要在榜上前幾名，票房反應都不差。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.fanpiece.com/168edward/%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E7%A5%A8%E9%81%B8%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%85%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E5%89%8D3%E5%90%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%93%AA%E5%B9%BE%E9%83%A8%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-c1296173.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.fanpiece.com%2F168edward%2F%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25A7%258B%25E5%25AD%25A3%25E8%25A7%2580%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25BE%2585%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1-%25E5%2589%258D3%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2593%25AA%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1-c1296173.html&d=8W6UNhn1qrXi%2BJrxuTVLv6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=12735028\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.fanpiece.com/168edward/%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%A7%8B%E5%AD%A3%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E7%A5%A8%E9%81%B8%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%9F%E5%BE%85%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E5%89%8D3%E5%90%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%93%AA%E5%B9%BE%E9%83%A8%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-c1296173.html</a>"},{"pid":"74feb6544703837ea614fd9038254eb672b65784","tid":409423,"uid":49157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T06:24:51.000Z","msg":"kaihchan32-c@ad.cityu.edu.hk"}]}